msg: BUNCH of work to get all of the wsdl loading/parsing/extension stuff to only be done in WSDLManagerImpl.   (First part of moving/getting rid of META-INF/extensions.xml)

That said, removed ServiceInfo from SchemaInfo since it wasn't actually used.  Thus, the memory leak may have been gone just from that.
Make sure only the stuff from the actual wsdl is cached.   Aegis tends to modify things strangely causing other problems.
